<h1 align="CENTER">Summer Institute on Scientific Creationism</h1>

The Institute for Creation Research is holding a

3-day Summer Institute on Scientific Creationism on July 24-26

in San Diego.  Call the <a data-original-url="http://www.icr.org" data-wayback-date="" href="http://www.icr.org">Institute for Creation Research</a> at 619-448-0900

for more details.





